Female (IBSP 2332). Coloration (in alcohol) and body as in male. Total length 41. Collum 1.83 long, 5.42 wide. Telson 1.13. Cyphopods ( Figs 8 C–D) with thick bristles dispersed on each of the valves. Apical part of cyphopod concave, with the intermediate membrane projecting between the valves ( Fig. 8 D). Distribution. States of Paraná and Santa Catarina, Brazil, in areas containing the Brazilian Atlantic forest biome (
Por et al. 2005
).
